                        and two lateral pendants reaching the bottom of the page; interlaces, floral
                        and anthropomorphic motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d2">
                        <locus target="#15r">15r</locus> (incipit page of Text I-3): elaborate
